@node "System" "What do you need ?"

@{b}                BruceLee manual@{ub}
Documentation version 1.0 written on 27 September 2000

Playing BruceLee will require the following items.

@{b} Amiga computer@{ub}
@{b} 4 MB free Fastram@{ub}
@{b} 68020+ processor@{ub}
@{b} AGA graphics@{ub}
@{b} JoyStick@{ub}
@{b} Multiplayer mode requires a parallel adapter@{ub}
Recommended is a 68030+ with 4+ MB fastram.

If you're having problems starting the program, please inform us.

@endnode


