@node "Usage" "BruceLee usage"

@{b}                BruceLee manual@{ub}
Documentation version 1.0 written on 27 September 2000

Start the program by clicking on the icon. CLI command can also be
used. Wait a while to let the program unpack its contents.

@{b}You can exit the game anytime by pressing RMB !@{ub}

@{b}Options screen@{ub}
The options can be altered using joystick. 

@{b}Players@{ub}
The first option will enter the number of players, up to four players 
can be selected.

@{b}Game mode@{ub}
Game mode can be switched between Normal and Crazy

@{b}Starting level@{ub}
Choose the start level

@{b}Start game@{ub}
Select this one to start the battle.

Right,.. not much of a problem I assume!  :)
@endnode

